          "text": "Primordial Resources:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " The resources you will gain after the Bat-tle, if the BP card is in the Wound Stack.",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "5",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " \u0007",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "AT:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " The Aeon Trespass field, the Primordial’s supernatural resist-ance to harm. The higher the AT, the more Power  is required to wound it.",
