          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " \u0007",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": "Critical:",
          "marks": []
        },
        {
          "kind": "text",
          "text": " If you manage to deal a Critical Wound, you will deal a powerful blow to the Primordial. Read the flavor text and enjoy your spoils! You ",
